<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3741290>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–7. Drypetothrips korykis gen et sp. n. and galls. (1) Drypetes deplanchei leaf margin galls; (2) holotype head and pronotum; (3) meso and metanotum; (4) antenna; (5) prosternites; (6) tergite IX and tube; (7) pelta and tergites II–IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3741290/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

